    "3645c3a1-1980-474f-9bf8-31b61e1a5a88": {
      "type": "dynamic-rich-text",
      "settings": {
        "width": "wide",
        "title": "Return Policy",
        "text": "<p>If your shipment is lost, damaged, or has paint match issues, report it to us immediately using the form below. Our team at Partify will evaluate your request and issue a partial or full refund or resend the ordered item(s) if your request is valid. For damage and/or paint issues, we will require photos for our investigation.</p><p><strong>Our team will respond to your request outlining why or why not your request will be granted. If granted, you will receive a confirmation email. You can expect a refund within 5-10 business days, or replacement part(s) sent out within 5 business days after your request is granted.</strong></p><p><strong>Because our products are custom made for your vehicle, we will not accept “change of mind” returns. We will only accept a refund request if there is evidence our team was negligent in fulfilling your order.</strong></p><p><strong>Your refund request must be sent within 14 days of receiving your order.<br/><br/></strong>You can find more details related to our <a href=\"https://www.partify.store/24862916693/policies/refund-policy.html?locale=en-US\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Return Policy\">return policy here</a>.</p>",
        "heading_size": "medium",
        "text_alignment": "left"
      }
    },
